body:
{{champion:119}} 

Draven went on free week, and after playing him once i&#039;m in love. He hits like a truck consistently throughout the game, and has a pretty decent kit for staying alive and chasing kills. I can&#039;t work his ult for the life of me, but I am enjoying the Spinning Axes mechanic. {{champion:119}}

Anybody got any good videos/links they can post me to? I&#039;ve take a standard build of rushing {{item:1053}} and then {{item:1001}} , then buying a {{item:3031}} , finishing my {{item:3072}} , and then {{item:3035}} {{item:3006}} {{item:3046}} {{item:3046}} . This gets me some pretty good damage against squishies and allows me to fight tanks to death, albeit I would swap a PD for BORK if I need to fight a tank heavy team. This also allows for 90% crits, and the AWESOME thing about Draaaaaven&#039;s Q is that it can crit causing [tons of damage](http://s3.roosterteeth.com/images/ahwaffles51a817f125583.jpg).
